Mavin Records music sensation and Headies award nominee, Rema returns with a brand new EP titled “Bad Commando“. The Edo born singer once again shows his musical prowess and further proves that he’ll be in the music business for a long time. ‘Bad Commando‘ EP serves as a good follow up to his previous project tagged ‘Freestyle EP‘. The project comprises of four beautiful records which were titled ‘Lady‘, ‘Rewind‘ ‘Spaceship Jocelyn‘ and ‘Bad Commando‘. Watch Bad Commando below: 